{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YYYKrvBpaorwFWK2cTBtHz","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information I need. Let me create a comprehensive report:\n\n## Codebase Exploration Report\n\n### 1. EntityController & EntityService Files\n\n**EntityController**\n- **Path**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/controller/EntityController.java`\n- **Endpoints**:\n  - `POST /api/v1/entities/query` - Query failed entities with pagination\n  - `GET /api/v1/entities/{id}` - Get entity by ID\n  - `GET /api/v1/entities/{id}/display-status` - Get entity with display status mapping\n\n**EntityService (Interface)**\n- **Path**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/service/EntityService.java`\n- **Key Methods**:\n  - `Entity getById(Long id)`\n  - `void save(Entity entity)` / `void saveBatch(Collection<Entity> entityList)`\n  - `Pagination<Entity> queryFailedEntities(EntityQueryDTO req)`\n  - `boolean isProcessingFinished(Long entityId)`\n  - `boolean updateProcessingState(Entity fresh)`\n  - `List<Entity> findStuckEntities(Duration staleThreshold, int maxCount)`\n  - **Reprocess methods**:\n    - `MarkForReprocessResult markAllForReprocess()`\n    - `List<Long> findTopNIdsByReprocessState(ReprocessState state, int limit)`\n    - `EntityProcessLockInfo findProcessLockInfoById(Long id)`\n    - `boolean claimInitEntityForReprocess(Long id)`\n    - `boolean updateReprocessStateById(Long id, ReprocessState state)`\n\n**EntityServiceImpl**\n- **Path**: `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/service/EntityServiceImpl.java`\n- **Config Property**: `policy.reprocess.mark-init-batch-size:1000`\n- **Notable Implementation Details**:\n  - Uses `TransactionTemplate` for batch processing with `PROPAGATION_REQUIRES_NEW` to handle failures independently\n  - `markAllForReprocess()` uses